# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [Unreleased]
*Nothing new yet.*

## 1.0.0 - 2016-06-18
This version was released on Saturday, 18th of June 2016. It was the first
release of this Ansible Role bringing basic support to install Mattermost
on a private server running Ubuntu Linux (either "precise" or "trusty").

While development Mattermost 3.1.0 has been released so support for this
new minor version was added last minute.

### Added
- Support for Ubuntu 12.04 "Precise"
- Support for Ubuntu 14.04 "Trusty"
- Support for Mattermost 3.0.3
- Support for Mattermost 3.1.0

[Unreleased]: https://github.com/MetaSyntactical/ansible-role-mattermost/compare/v1.0.0...HEAD
